dc_title_s: [Wilkes Exploring Expedition maps, 1841]; by the U.S. Ex. Ex., Charles Wilkes, Esqr., Commander; U.S. Dept. of Commerce, National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration, National Ocean Survey.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures; depths shown by soundings. Binder's title. Sheets numbered 135 to 161. 38 maps on 27 sheets; 86 x 88 cm. or smaller. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
